title: Did Trump Quit Costco Membership in This Letter?
subtitle: A letter purportedly sent by former U.S. President Donald Trump to Costco spoke of "an eight-pound tub of coconut clusters" and rotisserie chickens.
author: Jordan Liles
vclaim: An image showed former U.S. President Donald Trump canceled his Costco membership in a letter dated Feb. 4, 2021.
